        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">üß© Complete Mobile Menu Code</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Copy this entire block and paste it in your <code>AdminNav.razor</code> file where the Step 12 comments
                are.
                This creates the sliding drawer with all your navigation links, user profile info, and sign-in/sign-out
                buttons.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-5">
